{"prompt": "Generate a website for a financial consulting. The website should be professional and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Elite Financial Consulting</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #003366; /* Dark Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #e0e0e0; /* Light Gray */\n            --accent-color: #005299; /* Medium Blue */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            margin-top: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero-section {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.8), rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.8));\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .services-section,\n        .about-section,\n        .contact-section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .services-section h2,\n        .about-section h2,\n        .contact-section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item, .contact-info {\n            background-color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            margin: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover, .contact-info:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item p, .contact-info p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .about-content {\n            max-width: 900px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .about-content p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-section {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-section h2 {\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            background-color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 40px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid #cccccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Ensures padding doesn't affect width */\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 25px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            .hero-section h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .services-section h2, .about-section h2, .contact-section h2 {\n                font-size: 1.8em;\n            }\n            nav a {\n                display: block;\n                margin: 10px 0;\n            }\n            .services-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Elite Financial Consulting</h1>\n            <p>Strategic Guidance for Your Financial Success</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Empowering Your Financial Future</h2>\n            <p>We provide expert financial advice and strategic planning to help individuals and businesses achieve their long-term goals. Trust us to navigate the complexities of finance with clarity and precision.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"services-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"services-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Investment Management</h3>\n                    <p>Tailored investment strategies designed to grow and preserve your wealth, aligned with your risk tolerance and financial objectives.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Financial Planning</h3>\n                    <p>Comprehensive financial plans covering retirement, education, estate planning, and risk management for a secure future.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Corporate Finance</h3>\n                    <p>Expert advice on mergers, acquisitions, capital raising, and financial restructuring to optimize business performance.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Risk Assessment</h3>\n                    <p>In-depth analysis and mitigation strategies to protect your assets and ensure financial stability against market volatility.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"about-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Elite Financial Consulting</h2>\n            <div class=\"about-content\">\n                <p>Founded on principles of integrity, expertise, and client-centricity, Elite Financial Consulting has been a trusted partner for discerning clients for over a decade. Our team of seasoned professionals brings a wealth of experience from diverse financial backgrounds, enabling us to offer innovative and effective solutions.</p>\n                <p>We believe that strong relationships are built on trust and transparency. Our approach is collaborative, working closely with you to understand your unique challenges and aspirations. We are committed to providing personalized service and actionable insights that drive tangible results.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Elite Financial Consulting. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}